    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! \ud83c\udf1f I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly pristine, showroom condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied this thing since day one, and it\u2019s been kept spotless and shiny inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new and drives like a dream, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed! \ud83d\ude97\ud83d\udca8",
