    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade A80 Supra Turbo featuring the legendary 2JZ-GTE power plant. This example retains its original sequential twin-turbocharged configuration with pristine induction plumbing and factory-spec boost pressure. The drivetrain is anchored by the sought-after Getrag V160 six-speed manual transmission, delivering torque through a factory Torsen limited-slip differential. The chassis is exceptional, showing no signs of stress-fatigue, with all original factory spot welds and double-wishbone suspension components in concours condition. Compression across all six cylinders remains within nominal factory tolerances, and the undercarriage is free of any fluid seepage or oxidation. A true turn-key investment for the discerning collector seeking peak JDM engineering.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
