      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. Meticulously maintained and kept in a climate-controlled garage, the exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather is supple with no creases, and the original factory scent remains. Mechanically, it is flawless\u2014every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with full documentation provided. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this car represents the pinnacle of preservation. Ideal for the discerning buyer who demands the absolute best.",
