      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total showstopper! This beauty is in incredible, showroom condition\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot. It\u2019s been meticulously cared for, garage-kept, and is spotless inside and out. If you\u2019ve been looking for that 'perfect' find that drives like a dream and looks brand new, this is definitely it! I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions! \u2728",
