      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 Honda S2000 AP2, showcasing unparalleled mechanical integrity. This example features the high-revving F22C1 inline-four powerplant, delivering linear power through a precise close-ratio six-speed manual transmission. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity with the signature X-bone frame, complemented by a torque-sensing Torsen limited-slip differential for optimal power distribution. Meticulously maintained with all original VIN tags present, the double-wishbone suspension remains tight, and the VTEC engagement is flawless. This is a collector-quality specimen for the purist seeking a definitive analog driving experience.",
